  "2026-06-28T19:01:50.634Z",claude-code-agent,"PR #396 round-2 review: applied trim-before-dedup (CodeRabbit+Gemini) and resolver completeness for guide/completion/dedupe-audit/comments-audit (CodeRabbit Major). Barrel docstring + file-link nits (cubic) fixed. Greptile surface-change flag rebutted (144 exports identical main vs branch). MCP/CLI action-schema drift deferred to pm-zx13 (changes contract + needs per-param metadata)."
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-28T18:32:02.652Z",claude-code-agent,"Splitting the cli-contracts barrel: re-point the ToolOptionFlagContract type import in tool-option-contracts.ts from ../cli-contracts.js to the ./flag-contracts.js sibling (importing from the barrel while it re-exports tool-option-contracts is a cycle). Keep toUniqueFlagContracts exported from flag-contracts (tool-schema's _testOnlyCliContracts needs it) but OUT of the barrel re-export list so the public SDK surface stays unchanged. _testOnlyCliContracts (object literal) needs no docstring — the gate only requires docstrings on exported functions/interfaces/types."
